Pangolin precomputed scores dataset
-----------------------------------

Pangopup is designed to transform and query the following separately licensed
dataset:

  Title: Pangolin precomputed scores
  Creators: Nils Wagner and Aleksandr Neverov
  Publisher: Zenodo
  DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.15649338
  Source: https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.15649338
  License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
  License text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

The Pangopup index is a transformed representation of the source per-gene TSV
files. Pangopup may reorder, validate, index, and losslessly pack their numeric
fields for exact lookup. It does not change the source scores.

Distributed index bundles must retain this notice, identify the exact source
archive checksum, describe the transformation, and state whether further
changes were made.
